c. For each filtered field ũ_j, compute the eddy lifetime T_eddy(j) as the integral timescale of the wavelet-coefficient temporal autocorrelation at scale j:
   T_eddy(j) = ∫_0^∞ C_W(τ, j) dτ / C_W(0, j)
